commit.message: fixing bug on windows slash directory
fixing bug always show folder service or directori on call artisan
fixing bug create 2 directory on init
fixing empty folder in helper search file
add suport command api for generate service api
add support create repository with flag repository in make service
fixing bug make name repostiory with neseted path
remove query method in elequent implement
change service call interface to repository
add function to json in result service
add fitur auto make folder service
fixing type data on find or fail elequent in repository file
add record file error in catch data
Pretty print JSON in Express examples

server.js

I forgot to use 'server.js' in some of chapter 5's examples

Renumbered chapters

We moved chapter 3 (scraping) into the appendix, so lots of listings had
to be moved and renumbered.

Missing chapter 2 examples

Add some missing chapter 2 examples, and renumber the listings to be
three numbers (209 = listing 2.9, 210 = listing 2.10)

Command-line scripting: missing code

Add missing snippets, and fix things in Windows
Small improvements to the browser test samples
Make the async/sync test example clearer
Add examples for the Pug snippets

Chapter 8 fixes

Added some missing samples for hogan and fixed the existing hogan
example

Updates for chapter 8 (templates)

Add ejs snippets and fix some ejs API changes
Change Jade to pug in chapter 8
Listing updates based on Doug's feedback

Add server files for Connect examples

One of the reviewers found the examples were not easy to run without
suitable server files, so I've added them to the first four samples
Chapter 6 now has full examples for each framework
Cleaned up based on book content
Change example to use async, fix bug
Chapter 10: Original tests updated for ES6
The last set of listings from chapter 8
Add the listings for user registration and login
Updating the chapter 7 merged content listings
Add merged chapter 4/5 examples for Connect
Started adding the ES7 property bind syntax
Improve the way headers line up
Refactor the Electron app to use external css/js
The final set of examples from chapter 8
The last set of chapter 5 examples from chapter 7
Imported and fixed all listings from chapter 2
More chapter 2 listings imported and tested
Remove the old example that became tldr
Add shrinkwrap and package.json for listing 2
